Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The 88 Stars of the Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:05.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Urano Meteoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:25.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:32.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:45.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of admired this powerful world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:50.19,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chock-full of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:56.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Frozen time has started to move again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:01:02.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:08.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we born? Why do we live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:13.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any complicated answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:19.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.78,0:01:24.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple feelings are the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:32.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:39.53,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's cast a smile spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki! Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:13.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... won't... lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oracion Seis... doesn't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recollections of Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I have no power at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:38.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey... Why is she so beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One woman, one kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast away to oblivion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:19.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To disappear into the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...like an angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said sky, not water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out your hand, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Rapids?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it a sec... You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Angel has fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your death will not be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The extinction of the light will begin soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait... Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, there is no such thing \Nas freedom in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Erza go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... I don't know \Nhow I should face him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:48.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that Nirvana is a magic that \Ncan change people's personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The first stage is that black light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which forcibly changes anyone trapped \Nin the boundary between good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that you were in \Nthe gap between good and evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I was doing something a bit \Nwrong in the name of earning money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed pretty happy about it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all for my long-lost brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All to search for my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was for that I wanted money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:38.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at you, I remember the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... Are you saying I \Nresemble your brother, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the spitting image of the \Npotatoes my brother used to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's stop Brain and the others \Nfor the sake of love! Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck has been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,None of my magic has...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Air Magic, Aerial Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring. Isn't there anyone stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I shouldn't have come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:41.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still saying that, Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those negative feelings will get \Nyour heart stolen by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:52.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I ran away leaving Lucy-san \Nand the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you wouldn't \Nhave been any help regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But without you here, Erza would be dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we weren't able to find Nirvana either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were happy to be able to \Nmeet that Jellal person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is with Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said he saved your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never heard anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... I never told you, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Dragon, Grandine, vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was wandering along the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:46.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandine... Where are you, Grandine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:11.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was how we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in the middle of traveling, \Nand told me that he was lost as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:42.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So for the next month, we continued \Ntraveling together with no destination in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:58.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on a nasty day like \Nthis, some good can come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you pick them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... Where would be nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I tag along with you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he said something \Nweird all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I wanna come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. It'll be dangerous if you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I don't want to leave you, Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you head past this \Nforest, there's a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll take care of you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I was taken in by the guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and that was Caitshelter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what happened to Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never met him afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard rumors later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About how a council member \Nthat looked just like Jellal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,had done a bunch of really \Nbad things recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was really nice back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:07.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Jellal remembers me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza? She was revived?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that {\;1}I{\;0} didn't \Nnotice she was so close?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere until the \Nmain body of Nirvana starts up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:13.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...za...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:20.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything except that word...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me? Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:42.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lost all his memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Gray?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to me! I'll save Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no one's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lost all his memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:27.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For I am Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were once my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:15:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you went mad, desecrated \Nthe dead, hurt your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and even destroyed the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are trying to say you forgot that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then I will thrust a blade into your \Nchest and engrave it into your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really that Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:02.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A bandage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, what's with these clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:10.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are items from the Spirit World.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As yours were quite in tatters...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave Natsu-sama a matching outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}really{\i0} isn't necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal! Where's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's close. And wait, \Nhasn't the color changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:36.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. While you two were unconscious, \Nit changed from black to white.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He llllikes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you quit it with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where's Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have not seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:01.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, weren't you with Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:06.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... I guess the two of us \Nshould head to that light ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, I will now take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Virgo just passed through the \Ngate using her own magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do I have zero magic power left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:33.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:37.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you! Weren't you on Galuna Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where's doggy and 'brows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many episodes back that was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:45.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, Fairy Tail wizards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Damn you! You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting revenge for Lyon-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:08.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been acting all weird \Nafter that light appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting pretty weird before too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:11.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, that was a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you! Revenge for Lyon-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge for who exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Reports of my death are greatly exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a stubborn one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was pretty close...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:34.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's bomb lacrima was \Nmore powerful than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a long time before \NI was able to move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, he's stubborn all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not as stubborn as this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You jump down his throat for {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank... goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, she was \Ntaken over by something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nirvana...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The black pillar has turned white!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:21.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibiki, wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everyone is okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I get that you don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I wasn't able to \Nhear your thoughts at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you manage to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:50.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why did you unlock Nirvana's seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard someone's voice while I was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It said, "We are going to obtain Nirvana."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I dimly remembered the place \Nwhere that magic was hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dangerous magic. It \Ncan't fall into anyone's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I released the \Nseal... To destroy it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To destroy Nirvana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already set up the magic \Ncircle of self-destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:27.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana will shortly destroy itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:40.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this \Nhigh-level magic circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:44.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Nirvana will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal! Spit out the cancellation code!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the kindness from that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel kindness, \Ncheerfulness, and warmth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:13.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll continue to hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:17.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't help that... It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But hatred will steal the \Nfreedom from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It will eat away at you from within...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be free from Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take your hatred \Nand sadness... with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's attached a magic circle of \Nself-destruction to his own body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:11.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are... free!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:20.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do? Nirvana has been resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:00.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's got legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Nirvana was actually an octopus?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an octopus, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.32,0:24:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a squid?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, squid, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop squidding around and go already?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you got the wrong show!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.94,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: March of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:19.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I was trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.67,0:24:21.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll leave him here and go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.14,0:24:26.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
